Corporate Profile
Harmonic offers a comprehensive, innovative, and market-leading portfolio of video infrastructure products backed with world-class service plans and a global network of local support locations.
Today’s cable, satellite, telecom, Internet, and mobile service providers are engaged in an intense competition to offer a more extensive, personalized, and compelling video experience. Simultaneously, broadcasters, media content owners, and aggregators are seeking new ways to streamline their workflows and innovative business models for cost-effectively distributing their content. Harmonic addresses the evolving needs of the leaders in these different markets.
With its solutions for cable edge and access, video processing, and production and playout, Harmonic helps its customers to efficiently create, prepare, and deliver differentiated, high-quality video services while simplifying end-to-end asset management, reducing capital and operating expenses, and streamlining workflows.














