Products Powerful technology for today’s demanding media environments











Comprehensive IP Video Architecture
The video world is changing at a rapid pace. Harmonic helps content and service providers keep up — and stay ahead of the curve. We offer the industry’s most comprehensive portfolio of video delivery infrastructure solutions, all optimized to make your production, distribution and delivery networks more efficient, less expensive to operate, and capable of delivering superior-quality video to any device.
Harmonic video infrastructure solutions embrace all steps in the video delivery chain. Encompassing a broad portfolio of award-winning and industry-leading video processing, storage and cable edge products, a comprehensive Harmonic IP architecture addresses the complete range of contemporary and next-generation video services, from cloud media processing to the explosive growth of on-demand video delivery to mobile devices.

 








